Still other clients have tried to combine the two approaches‚Äîhiring an AV production company and a ‚Äúwebcasting specialist.‚Äù This approach inevitably fails too, as having two separate vendors accountable for¬†the success of a hybrid event means no one is ultimately accountable, and the reconciling of their different approaches and skill sets often degrades to finger-pointing when problems arise.

